<template>
  <v-card>
    <v-container fluid class="grey lighten 5">
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title>
          Template Management
        </v-card-title>
      </v-card>
      <v-card
        v-for="(templateType, index) in templateTypes"
        :key="index"
        class="pa-2">
        {{templateType}}
        <TemplateSelector
          :templateType="templateType"
        />
      </v-card>
    </v-container>
  </v-card >
</template>

<script>
import TemplateSelector from "@/components/templatemgmt/TemplateSelector.vue";

export default {
  name: "Templates",
  data() {
    return {
      templateTypes: [
        "Platforms",
        "Platform Names",
        "Platform Fees",
        "Portfolios",
        "Investments",
        "Investment Names",
        "Asset Allocation Names",
        "Risk Profiles",
        "Themes",
        "AFSLs",
      ]
    };
  },
  components: {
    TemplateSelector,
  },
  methods: {
  },
  mounted() {
  }
};
</script>
